works.description: Earlier this month, Car Design Fetish launched the Batmobile Design Competition, a design competition centered around the Batmobile, with an aim to find enthusiasts who can create amazing designs for the vehicle used by the Dark Knight in his Gotham-saving enterprises. The results are out now, with Paul Denton as the winner of the US category and Matt Gould as the winner of the International category.
